title: Developer Schmooze
description: A CMS style blog site using handlebars.js and SQL where developers can create an account, publish posts, edit and delete posts, as well as comment on other user's posts.

title: Weather Buddy
description: The Weather Buddy app pulls in third party data from an opensource weather api that uses geographical data to pinpoint locations and provide current weather as well as a five day forecast for that specific location
